item.title: About
item.description: EuroPadel Luxembourg is a just a spontaneous, non-profit initiative, formed by sports and Padel enthusiasts. All promoters are residents in Luxembourg and surroundings, sharing the same objective, aiming to promote Padel in Luxembourg and the region nearby. This initiative is open for all those who want to support Padel in the region. It already counts with the very appreciated support from our friends of EuroPadel Brussels. Sign up with us to show your support for this projectWritten in Go, Hugo is an open source static site generator available under the Apache Licence 2.
